allorsUnifiedGood.name: NISSAN FV02
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
The integral power steering is designed for enhanced manoeuvrability and operates smoothly and safely.
The V02 consists of a two-stage towing bar for easy height adjustment and offers a standard 2-speed automatic transmission for easy and safe operation.
This tractor offers fast acceleration and has a high power engine for the highest levels of productivity.
An improved cooling system adds the value of strong reliability and the large tyres give a smoother overall ride. The towing partner can be customised in a range of platinum colours.
The instrument panel is large and easy to read for further efficiency. Finally, the design is compact enabling a small turning circle, being user friendly and efficient.
